{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 1325135, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 260695, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "你的自身经历吗？", "timestamp": 1616594887, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1325139, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 260695, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "几期了？", "timestamp": 1616594901, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1325141, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 260695, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "尽力而为，生老病死，人之常情，终究活着的人还得继续生活下去。", "timestamp": 1616594928, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1325145, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 260695, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 对啊，现在正在医院陪床，突然感觉人生黯淡无光，害怕失去父亲，又被巨大的经济压力折磨。", "timestamp": 1616594969, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1325185, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 260695, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "有。刚查出来。生老病死，帮不了什么，可以哭，哭完日子照过", "timestamp": 1616595288, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1325194, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 260695, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 不容易。我是初中时妈妈查出来的癌症，幸好是早期，现在她还算健康。当时对我的心理挑战很大，还小。", "timestamp": 1616595357, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1325195, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 260695, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "有，做完手术了，早期术后靶向药不给报销，家庭条件一般所以没吃药，提心吊胆怕复发", "timestamp": 1616595367, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1325196, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 260695, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "公开募捐，大家都还是很愿意帮助校友的。如果家庭困难可以申请助学金。建议和你辅导员聊聊", "timestamp": 1616595376, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1325199, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 260695, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "是的，Carol说得对，生老病死，没办法。自己扛，受不了就多方寻求帮助，找朋友聊，找心理中心。成年人的世界就是这样的，加油吧", "timestamp": 1616595416, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1325205, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 260695, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 靶向药确实很贵。我家条件还可以，之前我妈妈就一直在吃", "timestamp": 1616595454, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1325220, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 260695, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "有，目前晚期，正在治疗。", "timestamp": 1616595532, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1325227, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 260695, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "用药兼顾效果和成本吧，多和医生沟通用药方案，选择适合你们家庭的", "timestamp": 1616595564, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1325298, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 260695, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 对，我妈妈不是那种很敏感的突变，而且多原发病灶只做了一次基因检测，所以不知道吃靶向药是不是值得。如果进医保一千多肯定就吃了，但是走不了医保，一个月五六千，差不多就是我家月收入了，就怕吃靶向药收益没那么大，反而以后需要的时候没钱治病了。目前随访，吃点中药调理一下身体体质", "timestamp": 1616596039, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1325315, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 260695, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "找辅导员/院系申请一个大病补助", "timestamp": 1616596164, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1325320, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 260695, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "还有每年的日常助学金，也能有大几千", "timestamp": 1616596177, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1325326, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 260695, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 是乳腺癌吗 ？早期还是中期？现在是已经治好了吗？建议别乱吃中药。", "timestamp": 1616596210, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1325335, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 260695, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "既然dz这个情况的话我说说我的情况吧，大学期间家人查出癌症，胰腺癌，有医保另外我的家庭算中等水平，但胰腺癌谁也救不了，已经去世了，没办法的事", "timestamp": 1616596258, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1325365, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 260695, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "癌症的发病率其实并不低，尤其是随着年龄增加，得癌症几乎是必然的。我建议大家了解具体父母得的是什么癌症，发展到了哪个时期，癌症分型是什么，有什么可供使用的药，该去什么医院治疗（尽量去北京的肿瘤专科医院），不要使用中药、偏方。照顾好病人的情绪，同时自己也要注意身体。加油", "timestamp": 1616596465, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1325366, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 260695, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Francis: 肺癌，早期，但是是多原发，俩大的切了，有的很小的病灶没切干净。没想着吃中药治癌症，我妈失眠胃口差啥的，吃中药改善一下，哪怕没用就当心理暗示了", "timestamp": 1616596475, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1325397, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 260695, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 还好只是早期，早期预后一般都不差，只要定期检查，问题不大！但还是不建议吃中药，副作用较多。", "timestamp": 1616596785, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1325409, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Isabella", "pid": 260695, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "抱抱", "timestamp": 1616596892, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1325509, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Jason", "pid": 260695, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "抱抱", "timestamp": 1616597648, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1326471, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Kate", "pid": 260695, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "抱抱", "timestamp": 1616603799, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1326599, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 260695, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "首选协和，西肿 人民次之，不要去海淀医院之类的二流医院", "timestamp": 1616604638, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1326602, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 260695, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "(指手术)", "timestamp": 1616604665, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1328972, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Louis", "pid": 260695, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "抱抱", "timestamp": 1616649007, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1445356, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 260695, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "尽管还有两个月要毕业了，但是家里实在是没人照顾妈妈，我休学一年回家了", "timestamp": 1618300434, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 10, "pid": 260695, "reply": 27, "tag": null, "text": "有没有在读期间父母患了癌症的同学，感觉好难撑过去怎么办，家庭经济状况也不好。", "timestamp": 1616594815, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1618300434, "url": "", "vote": {}}}